title: "Like A Great Vintage Wine"
posting_body: with high ceilings and beautiful refinished  hardwood floors..
Large living room with decorative fireplace..   Large formal dining room ...
Remodeled Kitchen with full size refrigerator, gas range and pantry...
Rear porch and large back yard with plenty of green space.
Heat, water and 1 car garage w/remote control included in rent.... Laundry & storage locker on site ...
Great location one block from blue line "L" and minutes from downtown Oak Park ...  Security deposit and credit check required ...
Cats ok but no dogs ..  Available Now !!
